item.title: UBER
item.description: score:-60 Chances: Uber possesses the right combination of the two key ingredients for a likely earnings beat in its upcoming report. Risks: Uber was fined 10 million euros for infringement of privacy regulations regarding its drivers’ personal data, which could indicate regulatory and legal risks for the company.
